section.div: ☁️ Help me cover my server and domains costs

div.p: A hobbyist developer working on creative open-source projects.

ul.li: metrics, a svg infographics generator for your GitHub profile
itsudeno, a scriptable IT automation system similar to ansible
gracidea, a Pokémon 2D live map with animated characters

div.p: I also contribute to deno standard library sometimes, I'm the author of the following features:

ul.li: deepMerge function (along with output type inference)
assertObjectMatch function for partial object matching assertions
improved string diff in test results, including both lines and words diff displays
yaml custom schemas support, along with additional type support

div.p: You can also check my other works on simon.lecoq.io

p.em: 💕 sponsors may be displayed on various readme and release notes as a thank you (even if it's a one time contribution)
